                "role": "Factory function. Switches on aEvent->mClass (eMouseEventClass, eKeyboardEventClass, ePointerEventClass, etc.) to call the appropriate NS_NewDOM*Event() constructor, or falls back to NS_NewDOMEvent() for generic events. Also handles string-based creation (document.createEvent())."
              }
            ]
